    "(3.4)Is I onto?",
    "Is I an isomorphism of Banach spaces?",
    "If I is onto, then (since it is injective), it is also a Banach space isomorphism, which equates to an identification of the dual space (P d) * (up to constants).",
    "This would be a result akin to Wolffe's theorem on duality of flat forms [25, Section 5].In the following, we provide a simple characterisation of the surjectivity of I via a compactness statement.",
